
     NAME
          jcclose - close a 'jc'-formatted file 

     FORTRAN F77 SPECIFICATION
          integer function  jcclose(iu)
          integer*4 iu

     PARAMETERS

          INPUT:
          iu    = file unit, can range from 1 to 25

     RETURNS
         -1     = error
          0     = everything fine 

     DESCRIPTION
          jclose closes a file that has been opend by jcopen(3) 
          for reading and writing with jcwrite(3), jcread(3).
          For a short description of the alogorithm see jctools(3).

